THE GAME
--------

  'SoliTri' is a solitaire type of game, it is based on 'Tri-Peaks'
where the game board consists of 28 cards that are placed in 3 
overlapping pyramids. A card (the 'next' card), facing up is shown
at the bottom under the game board. At the left of that card is a
pack of the remaining cards and that pack is face down.

  The goal of the game is to empty all the game board by clicking
on cards that are higher or lower by one unit than the 'next card'
in the bottom of the window. For example, if the card is a 7 of 
Heart, the choosen card should be a 6 or 8, the colour or type of
figure has no importance. Please note that in this game, a King
can follow an Ace and vice versa.

  Have fun!

